parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also lead to loss of vehicle control, which can result in crashes or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly
often without warning
and may continue to accelerate even when the brakes are applied. In some cases
the vehicle may also shift into reverse gear or experience sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake booster pump assembly failure can cause loss of braking power, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also lead to unintended acceleration, which can result in crashes or near-misses.
symptoms: The brakes may feel soft or spongy
or the vehicle may experience sudden loss of braking power. In some cases
the vehicle may also experience unintended acceleration or strange noises when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: DRCC malfunction can cause sudden and unexpected braking, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also lead to loss of vehicle control, which can result in crashes or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle may suddenly apply the brakes for no apparent reason
often without warning. In some cases
the vehicle may also experience sudden acceleration or deceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays in safety recalls can cause owners to continue driving vehicles with known safety defects, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Owners may experience frustration and concern due to delays in receiving safety recall repairs
which can lead to a lack of trust in the manufacturer and the safety of their vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy to cushion the impact.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
failure to stop the vehicle in time
abnormal sound when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or near-misses, and potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
vehicle fails to stop immediately
abnormal sound when braking
brake pedal goes to the floor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the paint can lead to rust and corrosion, which can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle and affect its overall appearance.
symptoms: Paint peeling on the right side and rear of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the PCS can cause the vehicle to suddenly brake, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes without warning
the PCS warning buzzer sounds
the vehicle's brakes are applied automatically
the vehicle's speed is reduced unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal travels to the floorboard
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the brake sensor warning light illuminates
the vehicle fails to stop immediately.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can leave vehicles with safety defects on the road, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The part to repair the safety defect is unavailable
the manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
the vehicle owner is unable to get the recall repair done in a timely manner.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the windshield along the perimeter can cause reduced visibility, increased risk of injury, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Glass delamination in various spots along the entire perimeter of the windshield
reduced visibility.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially if the vehicle is unable to be stopped.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration
loss of control
failure to stop despite braking
whirring sound from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaks in the sunroof or windshield can cause water damage, corrosion, and reduced visibility, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Unknown leaking
water entering the vehicle through the sunroof or windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PCS can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially if the system fails to alert the driver or incorrectly triggers.
symptoms: False warnings
incorrect triggering of the PCS
failure to alert the driver
system malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to address recall issues can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as well as reduced trust in the manufacturer.
symptoms: Failure to receive recall notices
lack of communication from the manufacturer
delayed or incomplete repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An electrical malfunction can cause the display panel to short out, leading to a loss of critical vehicle functions, including navigation, lights, and stereo systems, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially when driving at night or on the freeway.
symptoms: The display panel shuts down without warning
navigation and stereo systems fail
lights turn off
and the dashboard makes a clicking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle's ignition system can cause the vehicle to start without occupant assistance, and the rear deck lid can open while driving, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle starts without keys
the rear deck lid opens while driving
the starter is rough
hesitates
shutters
or the vehicle does not start without multiple attempts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PCS system can increase the risk of accidents, as it is designed to prevent or mitigate collisions.
symptoms: The PCS system is disabled
and the dealer is unable to repair or provide a fix date.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle stalling without warning can increase the risk of accidents, especially when driving at low speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
especially when preparing to make a turn.
